     FAKBPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FMCENP13 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PL18 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDGWP67 O   E                    DISK
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     E                    COM         4 12               COMPONENT PART
     E                    NEC         4  1 0             NECESSARY QTY.
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  48 COM
     I                                        1   5 A21HB5
     I                                        6  10 A22HB5
